Package com.activity.appligow

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateEventActivity
    The CreateEventActivity is an Activity class which is use by the user to create a new event.
    EventEditActivity
    The EventEditActivity is an Activity class used to modify the informations of an event.
    EventInformationsActivity
    The EventInformationsActivity is an Activity class that is used to show the informations of an event.
    EventsUserActivity
    The EventsUserActivity an Activity class used to show the several events of one user.
    HomeLoadingActivity
    The HomeLoadingActivity is an Activity class that display a waiting layout before the application is ready to be used.
    MainMapActivity
    The MainMapActiviy displays the main screen of the application, with the Google Map with which the user can interact.
    SignInActivity
    The SignInActivity is an Activity class used by the user to sign in.
    SignUpActivity
    The SignUpActivity is an Activity class used by the user to sign up.
    UserEditActivity
    The UserEditActivity is an Activity class used to update the user informations.
    UserInformationsActivity
    The UserInformationsActivity is an Activity class that displays the user informations.
